00:31:36.570 --> 00:31:39.170
Now we do have two
microphones available

00:31:39.170 --> 00:31:45.752
if anybody is interested in
and willing to ask a question.

00:31:45.752 --> 00:31:47.460
I'm always very grateful
to whoever will.

00:31:47.460 --> 00:31:49.459
I never ask questions
